  "title": "Clinical Research Nurse Co-ordinator ( East ) #HCT",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Responsibilities</strong></u></p><p>You will assist the principal investigator to develop and implementation:</p><p>\tTo prepare documents for and facilitate regulatory Approvals</p><p>\tTo facilitate the signing of project agreements with external collaborators.</p><p>\tTo implement and monitor programme activities and workflow.</p><p>\tTo facilitate programme-related outreach events and training sessions.</p><p>\tSubject's consent taking</p><p>\tScheduling study-related appointments for research subjects</p><p>\tCompleting data collection forms</p><p>\tConducting surveys or questionnaires</p><p>\tManaging the study-related equipment</p><p>\tHandling queries by research subjects</p><p><br /><u><strong>Requirements</strong></u></p><p>\tDegree in Nursing, Biological Science, Pharmacy or other healthcare related discipline.</p><p>\tAble to work independently</p><p>\tAble to adapt in a fast-paced environment</p><p></p><p>Interested candidates please send in your resume to:</p><p><u><strong>clinicalresearch@recruitexpress.com.sg</strong></u></p><p></p><p>EA Personnel: Valerie Yong Kian Fung</p><p>CEI No.: R1103704</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd, EA License No.: 99C4599</p>",
